[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]

[[module css]]
:root {
    --five-color: 196,2,51;
    --four-color: 255,109,0;
    --three-color: 255,211,0;
    --two-color: 0,135,189;
    --one-color: 0,159,107;
}

.color-five {
    background-color: rgb(var(--five-color));
}

.color-four {
    background-color: rgb(var(--four-color));
}

.color-three {
    background-color: rgb(var(--three-color));
}

.color-two {
    background-color: rgb(var(--two-color));
}

.color-one {
    background-color: rgb(var(--one-color));
}

.color-gray {
    background-color: rgba(var(--gray-monochrome, 66, 66, 72),0.15);
}

.color-white {
    background-color: rgb(var(--white-monochrome, 252, 252, 252));
}

.color-black {
    background-color: rgb(var(--black-monochrome, 12, 12, 12));
}

.icons {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, calc((100% / 5) - 0.25rem));
    grid-gap: 0.25rem;
}

.class-table-box {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 75%;
    background-color: rgb(var(--black-monochrome));
    grid-gap: 0.125rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.class-table-box > div {
    padding: 0.5rem;
}

.class-name {
    font-family: var(--title-font);
    font-size: 1.15em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}

.class-description {
    background-color: rgb(var(--white-monochrome));
}

@media (max-width: 500px ) {
.icons {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, calc((100% / 3) - 0.25rem));
}
}

.icon_image {
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 0.25rem solid rgb(var(--black-monochrome, 12, 12, 12));
    overflow: hidden;
}

.icon_name,
.icon_link {
    font-family: var(--title-font);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center; /* 中文调整 */
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

h1, h2 {
    text-align: center;
}

.step_container {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    border: 1px solid #999;
    padding: 1em;
}

.help {
    display: flex;
    align-content: stretch;
    padding-top: 1em;
    border-top: 1px dashed #999;
}

.help blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 85%;
}

.help blockquote > p {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    align-content: center;
    margin-right: 0;
    min-height: 2rem;
    margin: 0;
}

.help blockquote > p * {
    margin: 0 0.1rem;
    height: 100%;
}

.help blockquote:nth-of-type(1) {
    width: 50%;
    background: transparent;
    border: unset;
    box-shadow: unset;
    text-align: right;
    margin-right: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

.help blockquote:nth-of-type(1) > p {
    justify-content: flex-end;
}

.help blockquote:nth-of-type(2) {
    margin-left: 1em;
    width: 50%;
}

#page-content > .collapsible-block {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.75em;
    background-color: lightgrey;
    border-top: 0.125rem dashed slategrey;
    border-bottom: 0.125rem dashed slategrey;
}

#page-content > div.collapsible-block > div.collapsible-block-unfolded > div.collapsible-block-content {
    text-align:left;
}
[[/module]]

+ **异常分类栏**

------

[[div class="step_container"]]
+ [/anomaly-classification-system-guide 使用前请先阅读此指南]。
++ 欲了解在世界观内使用的理由，请阅读由 [[*user djkaktus]] 所写的[/classification-committee-memo 这份备忘录]。
[[=]]
+++ 此组件不必与黑色标记笔主题一起使用
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="step_container"]]
++++ 此系统主要由 [[*user woedenaz]] 编撰，此外也得到了许多、许多其他作者的帮助。

**特别感谢以下各位（排名不分先后）：**[[*user The Great Hippo]] | [[*user Rounderhouse]] | [[*user djkaktus]] | [[*user Yossipossi]] | [[*user Captain Kirby]] | [[*user CadaverCommander]] | [[*user Uncle Nicolini]] | [[*user aismallard]] | [[*user Jade Skylar]] | [[*user Lt Flops]] | [[*user Sterbai]]

++++ 这是一个非常富有挑战性的项目，我真的很感激我所收到的所有精彩的、有用的反馈。如果你帮助了我，而我没有在上面提到你，请务必告诉我！
[[/div]]

